org.cef.handler

Class CefKeyboardHandlerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cef.handler.CefKeyboardHandlerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CefKeyboardHandler 

    public abstract class CefKeyboardHandlerAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements CefKeyboardHandler
    An abstract adapter class for receiving keyboard events. The methods in this class are empty. This class exists as convenience for creating handler objects.(用于接收键盘事件的抽象适配器类。此类中的方法为空。此类的存在是为了方便创建处理程序对象。)

        Description copied from interface: CefKeyboardHandler

        Specified by:
        onPreKeyEvent in interface CefKeyboardHandler
